  "texts": [
    "The Visual USMLE dataset was created by adapting problems from the Amboss platform (using licensed user access), and it contains 618 questions.",
    "There is one image associated with each question.",
    "Each question can have up to 10 answer choices, but only one of them is correct.",
    "PromptThe following is the prompt used as the input to GPT-4V.You are an AI doctor trained in general medicine.",
    "You are given a medical question and an image as context, together with a list of possible answer choices.Only one of the choices is correct."
  ]
}